# ✅ To-Do Web Application

**Intern:** Utkarsh  
**Task:** Level 2 — Task 3  
**File:** `To_Do.html`

## 📌 Overview
A full-featured To-Do web app to manage daily tasks with pending/completed sections, priority levels, edit/delete functionality, and timestamps.

## 🎯 Features
- ✅ Add tasks with title, description, and priority
- ✅ Tasks visible immediately after adding
- ✅ Mark tasks as complete — moves to Completed section
- ✅ Pending Tasks section
- ✅ Completed Tasks section (with strikethrough)
- ✅ Edit any task via modal dialog
- ✅ Delete any task
- ✅ Tab filter — All / Pending / Completed
- ✅ Bonus: Timestamp when task is added
- ✅ Bonus: Timestamp when task is completed
- ✅ Bonus: Priority badges — High / Medium / Low
- ✅ Input validation

## 🖥️ Tech Stack
| Technology | Usage |
|------------|-------|
| HTML5 | Structure |
| CSS3 | Dark theme, grid, modal |
| JavaScript | CRUD operations, timestamps, DOM |

## 🚀 How to Run
Open `To_Do.html` in any browser — no installation needed.

